OL,3,CCouncil apologises after incorrectly
OL,4,Cissuing 6,000 parking fines
OL,6,FReading Borough Council has apologised
OL,7,Fto more than 6,000 motorists for
OL,8,Fincorrectly issuing parking fines over
OL,9,Fa number of years.
OL,11,FThe council discovered the Traffic
OL,12,FRegulation Order (TRO) on sections of
OL,13,Fthe East Reading Red Route and some
OL,14,Fparking restrictions in other
OL,15,Flocations are unenforceable.
OL,17,FA total of 6,136 penalty charge
OL,18,Fnotices (PCNs) were incorrectly issued
OL,19,Fand paid primarily between July 2018
OL,20,Fand 2024 with some dating back to 2013.
