OL,3,CCouncil apologises after incorrectly
OL,4,Cissuing 6,000 parking fines
OL,6,FThe council says drivers who have paid
OL,7,Fthese penalties will be reimbursed
OL,8,Fcosting the authority an estimated
OL,9,F#357,000.
OL,11,FFor motorists that have been subject
OL,12,Fincorrectly to a debt recovery
OL,13,Fprocess, the council says it will
OL,14,Fcontact individuals directly, telling
OL,15,Fthem how the repayment will be made
OL,16,Fwith interest.
